fields.title: About us
fields.description:
Kanatis LLC is a consulting firm in Baku, Azerbaijan established by professional consultants. We provide wide range of legal, tax, accounting, human resources and business consulting services. Alongside of its well known quality, our services are practical and fast for very reasonable comparable fees. 

We have extended experience in business formation and set-up, corporate and various commercial deals, contracts under Azerbaijani law, as well as excellence in taxation, customs and tax and customs consultancy services.

fields.name: Isa Tahmazov
fields.desc: Isa Tahmazov is Managing Partner at Kanatis LLC. He possesses LL.B degree from Baku State University and LL.M degree in International Commercial Law from the University College London (UCL). Mr. Tahmazov has worked as a lawyer for several local companies as in house lawyer and consultant before joining Kanatis. He is an experienced lawyer with a broad knowledge in company and commercial law, international transactions, as well as, state regulations and compliance.

fields.name: Nadir Mehdiyev
fields.desc: Mr. Nadir Mehdiyev is a Corporate Lawyer possessing LLB degree from Baku State University. Mr. Mehdiyev has 3 years of experience in corporate law. He has worked as a corporate lawyer for some leading local law firms and companies. Mr. Mehdiyev is also experienced in international arbitration proceedings. He is well experienced in corporate law, company law, contract law, employment law and migration law.

fields.name: Nuray Rustamova
fields.desc: Nuray Rustamova is financial analyst at Kanatis. She worked as financial analyst in the retail Industry which invested by foreign shareholders for more than before joining Kanatis, ultimately gaining experience in finance,sales,accounting,marketing as well as project management at a variety of levels. Recently, I have graduated from Master degree of Finance course at Siena University. Furthermore, she possess F1, F2 exemptions as well as F3 CBE certificate with 66 % score from ACCA Qualification.
